. React aur ReactDOM ka relation

React (library) â†’ Yeh sirf components banane ka dimaag hai.

Jaise useState, useEffect, JSX, hooks, etc.

Ye bas virtual DOM tak kaam karta hai (yaani browser pe actual dikhane tak nahi jata).

ReactDOM (library) â†’ Yeh bridge hai jo React ke virtual DOM ko real browser DOM pe chipkataa hai.

Matlab jo tumne <App /> banaya, woh ReactDOM ke bina screen pe kabhi dikh hi nahi paayega.
